  "title": "Construction Manager (Renovation) (Up to $6500)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Construction Manager (Renovation) (ID67171)<br />Location: Work on Site<br />Working Hours: Mon to Sat, 8.30am-5.30pm (work on site)<br />Salary: $5000-$6500<br />Benefits：AL from 14days, AWS<br /><br />Job Description<br />• Manage renovation and construction projects from start to finish.<br />• Supervise site progress, materials, and workmanship.<br />• Coordinate with relevant parties and ensure projects meet timelines, budgets, safety, and quality standards.<br />• Conduct site inspections and document defects.<br />• Assist in preparing shop drawings, project schedules, and reports.<br />• Support risk assessments and communicate safety measures to workers.<br />• Manage and coordinate subcontractors and workers.<br />• Handle Variation Orders (VO) and other assigned duties.<br /><br />Requirement:<br />• Relevant technical knowledge and experience in construction/renovation projects.<br />• Strong site management, coordination, and supervision skills.<br />• Familiar with safety, quality standards, and risk management.<br />• Ability to manage teams and work in both office and site environments.</p>",
